    {
      "id": "609656",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "fb_china_today",
        "uid": "8633"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t那需要巨大的动员力。<br/>\n<br/>\n现在这么一闹, 我目测党国已经没有那个力量, 只能迁就形式<br/>\n<br/>\n中国人拿出少少的勇气就可以让他们滚蛋(什么都不做依然不行)\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-12-12",
      "agree_count": 0,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "609657",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "一九四二",
        "uid": "101140"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t想不想做和做不做的到是两回事，它只能想想而已了。\t\t</div>",
